                <note rend="inline" type="source">800.8820/922: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-01-09T21:00:00-04:00"
                            >January 9, 1942 [<hi rend="italic">1943</hi>]—9 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>27. Owing to the liberal licensing policy of the Board of Economic Warfare with
                    respect to exports to the other republics there are now produced very
                    substantial quantities of materials which are awaiting shipment. With regard to
                    certain countries, including that to which you are accredited, the backlog of
                    goods now licensed and produced exceeds the available shipping space for many
                    months.</p>
                <pb facs="0172" n="160" xml:id="pg_160"/>
                <p>The composition of this backlog and the tonnages involved are summarized as
